According to the website Celebrity Net Worth, Bill Mahers salary is $10 million per year, and his net worth is pegged at approximately $100 million. So, if a recession comes, even if Mr. Maher loses his job, hes not exactly going to be sleeping on a park bench.

How easy it is to say, Sorry if that hurts people, when its other people youre wanting to see get hurt, knowing all along that youll be just fine, thank you very much!